Invocation Name: calorie counter
des:
With Simple Calorie Counter you can keep track of how many calories you are consuming each day. Every day it will automatically reset back to zero

Features to come(in no specific order):
setting calorie target
setting weekly calorie target
checking weekly calories
modifying past days calories
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
